trans-unit.source: Represents the binding element for the named pipe transport.
trans-unit.target: Representa o elemento de associação para o transporte de pipe nomeado.

trans-unit.source: This transport uses URIs of the form "`net.pipe`://`hostname`/`path`".
trans-unit.target: Esse transporte usa URIs no formato "`net.pipe`://`hostname`/`path`".

trans-unit.source: Other URI components are optional.
trans-unit.target: Outros componentes do URI são opcionais.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.NamedPipeTransportBindingElement> class is the starting point for creating a custom binding that implements the named pipes transport protocol.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.NamedPipeTransportBindingElement> classe é o ponto de partida para criar uma associação personalizada que implementa o protocolo de transporte de pipes nomeados.

trans-unit.source: This transport is used for on-machine WCF communication.
trans-unit.target: Esse transporte é usado para comunicação de WCF na máquina.

trans-unit.source: The WCF service model uses this class to create factory objects that implement the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> interfaces.
trans-unit.target: O modelo de serviço WCF usa essa classe para criar objetos de fábrica que implementam o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelFactory> e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.IChannelListener> interfaces.

trans-unit.source: These factory objects then create and accept the channels that transmit SOAP messages using the named pipes protocol.
trans-unit.target: Esses objetos de fábrica, em seguida, criar e aceitam os canais que transmitem mensagens SOAP usando o protocolo pipes nomeados.

trans-unit.source: You configure the factories that this class creates by setting its properties, such as: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.NamedPipeTransportBindingElement.ConnectionPoolSettings%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Configurar as fábricas de que essa classe cria definindo suas propriedades, como: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.NamedPipeTransportBindingElement.ConnectionPoolSettings%2A>.

trans-unit.source: You can also set properties on the base class, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>, such as: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.MaxBufferSize%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.TransferMode%2A>, and <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.ConnectionBufferSize%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Você também pode definir propriedades na classe base, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>, tais como: <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.MaxBufferSize%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.TransferMode%2A>, e <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement.ConnectionBufferSize%2A>.

trans-unit.source: For a complete list of properties, see <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter uma lista completa das propriedades, consulte <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>.

trans-unit.source: Finally, you can set properties on the base class of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>, which is <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>, such as <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.MaxBufferPoolSize%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Por fim, você pode definir propriedades na classe base de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.ConnectionOrientedTransportBindingElement>, que é <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>, como <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement.MaxBufferPoolSize%2A>.

trans-unit.source: For a complete list of properties, see <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>.
trans-unit.target: Para obter uma lista completa das propriedades, consulte <xref:System.ServiceModel.Channels.TransportBindingElement>.
